aris]]'', ''[[Cries and Whispers]]'', ''[[Deep Throat (film)|Deep Throat]]'', ''[[Last Tango in Paris]]'', ''[[What's Up, Doc? (1972 film)|What's Up, Doc?]]'', ''[[Fritz the Cat (film)|Fritz the Cat]]'', ''[[Cabaret (1972 film)|Cabaret]]'', ''[[The Poseidon Adventure (1972 film)|The Poseidon Adventure]]'' \n* '''[[1973 in film|1973]]''' \u2013 ''[[The Exorcist (film)|The Exorcist]]'', ''[[Enter the Dragon]]'', ''[[Don't Look Now]]'', ''[[Badlands (film)|Badlands]]'', ''[[Amarcord]]'', ''[[The Sting]]'', ''[[Enter the Dragon]]'', ''[[Charlotte's Web (1973 film)|Charlotte's Web]]'', ''[[Mean Streets]]'', ''[[American Graffiti]]'', ''[[Paper Moon (film)|Paper Moon]]'', ''[[The Wicker Man]]'', ''[[Heavy Traffic]]'', ''[[Papillon (1973 film)|Papillon]]'', ''[[Fantastic Planet]]''\n* '''[[1974 in film|1974]]''' \u2013 ''[[A Woman Under the Influence]]'', ''[[The Godfather Part II]]'', ''[[Chinatown (1974 film)|Chinatown]]'', ''[[The Conversation]]'', ''[[Young Frankenstein]]'', ''[[Blazing Saddles]]'', ''[[The Texas Chain Saw Massacre]]'', ''[[Black Christmas (1974 film)|Black Christmas]]'', ''[[The Towering Inferno]]'', ''[[That's Entertainment!]]'', ''[[The Nine Lives of Fritz the Cat]]''\n* '''[[1975 in film|1975]]''' \u2013 ''[[Jaws (film)|Jaws]]'', ''[[One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest (film)|One Flew Over the Cuckoo's Nest]]'', ''[[Barry Lyndon]]'', ''[[Coonskin (film)|Coonskin]]'', ''[[Hedgehog in the Fog]]'', ''[[Dog Day Afternoon]]'', ''[[Nashville (film)|Nashville]]'', ''[[The Rocky Horror Picture Show]]'', ''[[Monty Python and the Holy Grail]]'', ''[[The Pinchcliffe Grand Prix]]'', ''[[Hans Christian Andersen's The Little Mermaid (1975 film)|Hans Christian Andersen's The Little Mermaid]]''; [[videocassette recorder]]s appear on mass market\n* '''[[1976 in film|1976]]''' \u2013 ''[[Taxi Driver]]'', ''[[Rocky]]'', ''[[Network (1976 film)|Network]]'', ''[[Carrie (1976 film)|Carrie]]'', ''[[All the President's Men (film)|All the President's Men]]'', ''[[The Smurfs an